{"word":"ἀμαθύνω","slug":"ἀμαθύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμαθύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄμαθος'><el>ἄμαθος</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to level with the sand, utterly destroy</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to spread smooth, level</i>, <el>κόνιν</el> h. <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}